(583, 'civicrm_contact', 1062, 'As an information, ICALTD became a member of AGRIS since the 1975''s. From that time we were actively sending agricultural research data bibliography in the ISO file format. Until now we are still processing the data by using the program CDS / ISIS for Windows (Winisis).\r\n\r\nWhen AGRIS system changes, we are not yet ready to follow. So we have difficulty in adjusting applications / programs used by the AGRIS (such as DSpace, Agrimetamaker etc.).\r\n\r\nFor that we make the display format (PFT files) on Winisis so that the output file as xml data that we send to you. Because we have not fully use application that has been provided by AGRIS.\r\n\r\nThe point is we want to update the data AGRIS, because approximately since 2005 until now, we have not updated anymore.\r\n', 1295, '2014-08-29', 'History & problem', '0'),
