(186, 676, 'The Chinese Agricultural Sci-tech Documents Database (CASDD) is a bibliographic/abstracts database that has been developed by CAAS-AII. The database provides the most important aggregation of records of agricultural science and technology information (journal papers, proceedings and other material) from Chinese research and educational institutions in terms both of volume and timespan covered.', NULL, NULL),
