(306, 796, '<p><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">R4D is a free access on-line portal containing the latest information&nbsp;about research funded by DFID, including details of current and past research in over 40,000 project and document records.</span></p>', 'GB', '1'),
(307, 797, '<p><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana, ''trebuchet ms'', trebuchet, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);">De Gruyter Open (formerly Versita) &nbsp;is one of the world&rsquo;s leading publishers of open access scientific content. Today De Gruyter Open (DGO) publishes about 400 own and third-party scholarly journals across all major disciplines.</strong></p>', 'PL', 'A'),
(308, 798, '<p><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">IRRI aims to reduce poverty and hunger, improve the health of rice farmers and consumers, and ensure environmental sustainability of rice farming.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'QR', '0'),
(309, 799, '<p>ProdInra is INRA institute&#39;s open access repository. ProdInra contains references and full text documents to publications authored by INRA researchers relating to Agriculture, Food and Environnment. ProdInra stores research results and provides a free access to some of them.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="field field-name-field-percentage-of-full-text field-type-list-text field-label-inline clearfix" style="margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Ubuntu, Arial, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n<div class="field field-name-field-percentage-of-full-text field-type-list-text field-label-inline clearfix" style="margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Ubuntu, Arial, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n<div class="field-label" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; float: left; display: inline; clear: left;">Percentage of full text:&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="field-items" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; float: left; display: inline;">\r\n<div class="field-item even" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 5px !important; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; display: inline;">Between 5% and 25%</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="field field-name-field-languages-covered field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline