(518, 1134, '<div class="expanding-formatter-summary" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Ubuntu, Arial, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px; display: inline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">The Center for Agricultural Information and Documentation has the following functions: Coordinate the implementation of the actions and policies established for documentation and public information in the Ministry of Agriculture to promote exchanges with other organizations in the field of documentation and information of interest to the agricultural sector; Guiding normative and methodological documentation services and information in different organs and institutions of the Ministry of Agriculture; Disseminate agricultural information to the technicians of the sector and the general public through written publications and other information services; Coordinate the development, registration and publication of documents of interest to the agriculture sector in the Ministry of Agriculture.</div>', 'MZ', '0'),
