(556, 1234, '<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Ubuntu, Arial, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">The SLU University Library comprises several units located at our main campuses&nbsp;in Alnarp, Skara, Uppsala and Ume&aring;. The organization also includes libraries in Skinnskatteberg and Flyinge.</span></p>', 'SE', '0'),
