(360, 1605, '<p>Forest Research and Management Institute&nbsp;&nbsp;(ICAS) is a national public institution with legal personality to the Ministry of Environment and Forests (Law No. 46/2008) specializes in research, technological development, investment planning, grant specialized technical consulting and implementation of new technologies to sustainable forest management.</p>'),
(361, 1606, '<p>The main components of the Faculty of Forestry activities are education and scientific research in forestry. Department fulfills its mission through continuous improvement of students in the spirit of advancement of knowledge and lifelong learning, active participation in the scientific and cultural universal, and by developing a strong inside or research teams that participate in the realization of scientific projects of scale and diversification of studies correlated with labor market needs. Faculty of Forestry of Suceava prepares for forest engineers with complex cultural activities forest exploitation and transportation of wood, primary industrialization and exploitation of timber.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');
